g.text: A Payer's SP calls this to remove an RTP registration.
Checks for a valid, non-expired JWT.
Subject in token matches the Service Provider ID in the record. Access is granted.
Moves the record to a separate collection for audit purposes.
The Payer can no longer receive RTPs.
The specified activation could not be found.
: Subject in token does NOT match the owner.
You do not have permission to delete this activation.
e.g., Database connection failure, unhandled exception.
